P_HTM[140]='*‘‘Ayaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto hoti kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko.*';
P_HTM[141]='*‘‘Ayaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu suvaco hoti…pe… anusāsaniṃ.*';
P_HTM[142]='*‘‘Ayaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu yāni tāni  sabrahmacārīnaṃ uccāvacāni kiṃkaraṇīyāni tattha dakkho hoti analaso tatrupāyāya vīmaṃsāya samannāgato alaṃ kātuṃ alaṃ saṃvidhātuṃ.*';
